SearchTheSummerAway generates different summer activities to get you moving and having a blast in the sun. Whether it be a sport, hobby, or and outdoor exercise, we have a bit of everything!

SearchTheSummerAway generates different summer activities to get you moving and having a blast in the sun. Whether it be a sport, hobby, or and outdoor exercise, we have a bit of everything! Use the To Do list to remove any activities.

SearchTheSummerAway was created during the SUNS OUT HACKS OUT hackathon hosted by Major League Hacking. Where the goal was to create a project during the weekend.
